1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=My Greatest Danger Is You=

4
00:00:48,070 --> 00:00:48,930
Che,

5
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,470
this matter ends here.

6
00:00:50,689 --> 00:00:52,216
Do not bring ruin upon the whole tribe.

7
00:00:53,350 --> 00:00:54,200
But...

8
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,390
There is no but.

9
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:58,280
Between the tribe and Wu Zhaoli,

10
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,400
you must make

11
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,710
a choice today.

12
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,310
(Perhaps cutting ties with me)

13
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,560
(is good for Che.)

14
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:19,790
(At least in the future,)

15
00:01:20,346 --> 00:01:21,790
(he won't have to struggle anymore.)

16
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:24,120
Your goal has been achieved.

17
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,150
We can leave now.

18
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:27,350
Fine.

19
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:28,819
Since you don't wish to stay here,

20
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,960
let's go.

21
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,350
From this day on,

22
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,200
Wu Zhaoli of the Wuyue tribe

23
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:39,230
will no longer be your wife.

24
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,840
Luo Cheng.

25
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:41,710
Yes.

26
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,200
Yan Che, take the decree.

27
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,270
Ying Du,

28
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,787
I never thought you'd care so much
for Zhaoli.

29
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,430
I was just troubled
about finding your weakness.

30
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,120
Ying Du,

31
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:23,910
this seat

32
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,520
should be shared by you and me.

33
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,310
Why is

34
00:02:36,910 --> 00:02:38,470
the one by your side now

35
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,590
someone else?

36
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:57,590
Ye Li.

37
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,750
Who are you?

38
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,750
Your Highness,

39
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,710
you're right.

40
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,560
The one meant to stand beside him
should have been you.

41
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:11,630
What do you want?

42
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:13,030
I want

43
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:14,560
to help you regain

44
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,280
what was lost.

45
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,080
You want to turn me against the ruler?

46
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,800
I'll never agree to that.

47
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,520
He is my elder brother.

48
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,560
Yet you share no blood ties with him,

49
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,430
do you?

50
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,120
Your heart has long been devoted to him,

51
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,750
yet you can only watch helplessly

52
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:30,190
as others take that place beside him.

53
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,910
I truly feel all these years

54
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,000
of devotion are undeserved.

55
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,560
Are you truly willing to let it go?

56
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,910
I dislike seeing other women near him,

57
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,710
but it is his choice to make.

58
00:03:43,887 --> 00:03:45,187
All I wish is for his well-being.

59
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:46,750
Then, do you realize

60
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,240
Wu Zhaoli is Saintess Xihe?

61
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,240
The Saintess is bound by fate.

62
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,750
She must never fall in love.

63
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,680
Otherwise, fate will punish her.

64
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,030
When that happens,

65
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,680
Ying Du's soul will also shatter

66
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:00,030
because of her.

67
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,590
The ruler

68
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,120
will lose his soul

69
00:04:03,590 --> 00:04:06,000
for that woman?

70
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,030
(In my second life,)

71
00:04:10,669 --> 00:04:12,213
(it feels like everything has changed.)

72
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:15,120
(Ying Du bears deep hostility
toward Che.)

73
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:17,070
(He keeps saying that Che will harm me.)

74
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,120
(Che seems burdened)

75
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,560
(with secrets he cannot share.)

76
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,830
(Everlasting Joy)
(What happened back then?)

77
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:38,230
Oracle,

78
00:04:38,241 --> 00:04:39,887
(Oracle)
do you know the Fengwu Bracelet?

79
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,430
The Bracelet is an ancient treasure.

80
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,190
It can turn back time.

81
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,160
(As long as I get the Bracelet,)

82
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,120
(I can uncover why he slew)

83
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,800
(Grandmother and the entire tribe.)

84
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,920
Ying Du.

85
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:00,590
Ying Du?

86
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:20,837
(That's the wound
I stabbed him with that day.)

87
00:05:21,703 --> 00:05:23,470
(Doesn't he have the power
to heal himself?)

88
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,390
(Why has it still not mended?)

89
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:27,680
(Forget it.)

90
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,360
(I'll find the Bracelet first.)

91
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:36,160
Why weren't you affected
by my calming incense?

92
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,000
Zhaoli,

93
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:38,630
whatever you're thinking,

94
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,040
don't dig any deeper.

95
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:42,190
The more you know,
the greater the danger.

96
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,430
My greatest danger is you.

97
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:46,160
What exactly are you hiding from me?

98
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,480
Why won't you say anything?

99
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:49,230
Zhaoli,

100
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:50,560
you only need to remember

101
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,920
that no matter what, I'll keep you safe.

102
00:06:03,183 --> 00:06:04,376
What's happening to your hand?

103
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,720
Are you worried about me?

104
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:08,720
Of course not.

105
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,560
Who said I'd worry about you?

106
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,510
(The Frostbite Curse
is striking more often.)

107
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,600
(It seems I won't last much longer.)

108
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,750
(I must repair the Bracelet soon.)

109
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,920
(That way, even if I'm gone,)

110
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,510
(the Bracelet can still protect Zhaoli.)

111
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,230
Your Majesty,

112
00:06:41,453 --> 00:06:43,166
Yan Che has begun to act,
just as expected.

113
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:46,000
He met Ye Li in secret last night.

114
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,600
Find out what they're after.

115
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,670
Yes.

116
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,640
Your Majesty,

117
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:57,720
your Frostbite Curse is worsening.

118
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,480
The Frost Seal is fading fast.

119
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,800
If you keep draining your power,
you may not survive.

120
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,640
It's nothing.

121
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,600
(The Bracelet.)

122
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,920
(I found it.)

123
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:21,720
What are you doing?

124
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:24,710
(Ying Du,)

125
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,546
(since you refuse to say anything,)

126
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:28,160
(I'll find out)

127
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:30,390
(what danger you were talking about.)

128
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,390
Could it be because it's damaged

129
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,150
that it shows no reaction?

130
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:12,750
I wonder if Oracle can help

131
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,750
awaken the Bracelet.

132
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:25,750
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

133
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:32,550
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

134
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:37,290
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

135
00:09:37,290 --> 00:09:40,190
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

136
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:46,000
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

137
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,700
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

138
00:09:50,050 --> 00:09:52,400
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

139
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:56,440
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

140
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,820
♪And that is enough♪

141
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:02,610
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

142
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:05,580
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

143
00:10:05,950 --> 00:10:11,700
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

